import React from "react"; const SalaryInsights = ({ insights }) => { const { salary_range, experience_levels } = insights; return (

Salary Insights

{/* Salary Range */}

Salary Range

Entry Level: {salary_range.entry_level}
Mid Level: {salary_range.mid_level}
Senior Level: {salary_range.senior_level}
{/* Experience Levels */}

Experience Requirements

{Object.entries(experience_levels).map(([level, years]) => (
{level .replace(/_/g, " ") .replace(/\b\w/g, (l) => l.toUpperCase())} : {years}
))}
); }; export default SalaryInsights;
